          <h2>Drain & Sewer Services</h2>
          <p>Each service below has its own page with detailed scope, signs to watch for, and the honest steps Honest Drain takes on the visit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="commercial-service-board"><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-drain-cleaning"><h3 id="group-drain-cleaning"><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/">Drain Cleaning</a></h3><article class="service-line"><span>01</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/emergency-drain-cleaning/">Emergency Drain Cleaning</a></h4><p>When a drain backs up after hours, an emergency response can stop water damage before it spreads. Honest Drain shows up prepared, explains the cause, and clears</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>02</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/basement-drain-cleaning/">Basement Drain Cleaning</a></h4><p>Basement floor drains are the last line of defense before water reaches finished floors. Honest Drain clears them, tests them, and explains how to keep them flo</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>03</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/pipe-descaling/">Pipe Descaling</a></h4><p>Cast iron drains in older homes choke on rust, mineral scale, and tubercles. Mechanical descaling restores the inside diameter without ripping out the pipe.</p></div></article></section><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-sewer-repair-and-replacement"><h3 id="group-sewer-repair-and-replacement"><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/">Sewer Repair and Replacement</a></h3><article class="service-line"><span>09</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/emergency-sewer-repair/">Emergency Sewer Repair</a></h4><p>A collapsed or separated sewer cannot be cleaned around. When sewage is surfacing or the line is unusable, emergency sewer repair restores service quickly.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>10</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/root-intrusion-repair/">Root Intrusion Repair</a></h4><p>Roots find the smallest gap and turn it into a root ball that catches every flush. Repair the joint or the cracked section and the line stops feeding the tree.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>11</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/sewer-backup-repair/">Sewer Backup Repair</a></h4><p>A sewer backup is the symptom of a damaged or restricted line. Repair the underlying defect and the backup does not return on the next heavy use day.</p></div></article></section><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-exterior-drain-services"><h3 id="group-exterior-drain-services"><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/exterior-drain-services/">Exterior Drain Services</a></h3><article class="service-line"><span>12</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/exterior-drain-services/driveway-drain-cleaning/">Driveway Drain Cleaning</a></h4><p>Driveway drains and trench drains catch the water that would otherwise pool against the garage door. Keep them clear and the water keeps moving.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>13</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/exterior-drain-services/landscape-drain-services/">Landscape Drain Services</a></h4><p>French drains, downspout extensions, and yard area drains all share the same job: move water somewhere it cannot hurt the house. Keep them open and they keep wo</p></div></article></section><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-septic-services"><h3 id="group-septic-services"><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/septic-services/">Septic Services</a></h3><article class="service-line"><span>14</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/septic-services/septic-tank-cleaning/">Septic Tank Cleaning</a></h4><p>A clean tank is the simplest way to extend the life of a leach field. Skipping cleanings sends solids into the field and shortens the system's useful life.</p></div></article></section><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-other"><h3 id="group-other">Other services</h3><article class="service-line"><span>04</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/hydro-jetting/">Hydro Jetting</a></h4><p>When cabling only opens a temporary path through grease, sludge, scale, or roots, hydro jetting cleans the whole pipe wall and resets the maintenance clock.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>05</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-and-sewer-inspection/">Drain and Sewer Inspection</a></h4><p>A drain and sewer camera tells the truth about the line. Belly, crack, root, scale, or collapse — the repair plan is based on evidence, not guesswork.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>06</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-repairs/">Drain Repairs</a></h4><p>When cabling and jetting are not enough, the drain itself needs work. Honest Drain repairs broken fittings, replaces failing sections, and corrects undersized l</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>07</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-sewer-maintenance/">Drain & Sewer Maintenance</a></h4><p>Most backups are predictable. A cleaning and inspection cadence built around how a home actually uses water keeps the small problems from becoming the big ones.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>08</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-cleaning/">Sewer Cleaning</a></h4><p>Main-line sewer clogs affect the whole home. Honest sewer cleaning clears the line, identifies the cause, and explains what to do next.</p></div></article></section></div>
